WEBVTT


00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.980
=Episode 36=

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.040
No problem.

00:01:39.800 --> 00:01:41.280
Before three o'clock,

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:42.600
I'll get you the script.

00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:43.640
Okay.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:46.800
Then let's go.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:02.440
You've missed work all week.

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:04.280
And now you want to perform?

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:06.440
Not a chance.

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.080
Troupe Leader.

00:02:08.920 --> 00:02:10.880
No, I told you already.

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:13.040
I've had a cold and a fever.

00:02:13.640 --> 00:02:15.160
It's been over a week.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:17.600
That old place I'm staying in

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.960
has drafty windows.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.800
It's nothing like the troupe's new rooms.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:25.280
Who do you think you're fooling?

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.640
Listen to me.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.000
The troupe has already decided.

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:30.960
For Hu Xian Jie,

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:33.400
the male lead is Xue Guisheng.

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:34.480
Stay out of it.

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:35.600
Who voted on that?

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:37.680
Yi Qin'e and Feng Zi?

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:40.240
Enough with all that nonsense.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.160
Casting in the troupe

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:44.160
has its own rules and process.

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:45.920
Fine.

00:02:47.320 --> 00:02:48.800
I've got my own way.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.600
What are you planning?

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:56.040
Just look at the state of you.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.560
Look at these lyrics.

00:02:57.600 --> 00:02:59.160
They fit Scholar Hu

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:01.440
in Hu Xian Jie so well.

00:03:02.160 --> 00:03:03.080
Yes. In my view,

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:04.440
Scholar Hu

00:03:04.520 --> 00:03:06.680
isn't a bold, brash character.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.880
He's thoughtful and meticulous.

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.440
Gentle at heart.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.040
But a bit indecisive.

00:03:12.040 --> 00:03:13.280
Exactly. We're on the same page.

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:14.960
I think the two should be switched.

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:16.640
The heroine should be the bold one.

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:19.040
And the hero is more delicate, right?

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:21.720
- Troupe Leader Yi, you agree?
- Yes.

00:03:21.720 --> 00:03:22.880
A true kindred spirit is rare.

00:03:22.880 --> 00:03:24.800
Troupe Leader Yi, that's you.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.200
I...

00:03:26.600 --> 00:03:28.080
Get your paws off her.

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:29.240
What are you doing?

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.240
Getting cozy in broad daylight?

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:33.240
Not afraid her man will bash you?

00:03:33.440 --> 00:03:35.040
We were discussing the lyrics.

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:36.760
Qin'e, Qin'e, listen.

00:03:36.920 --> 00:03:39.080
Let me return to Hu Xian Jie.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:41.840
We've done two shows together already.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.520
The troupe decides who performs.

00:03:43.520 --> 00:03:44.360
It's not up to me.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.360
Actors really have no heart.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:52.600
Two shows, and you've caught feelings?

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:54.160
What are you talking about?

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:55.880
Don't throw accusations at us.

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:57.480
What am I talking about?

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:00.280
You, Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera,

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:02.000
how is your taste...

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.040
like this?

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:06.280
You ditched us first.

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:08.040
Know what "Art above all else" means?

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:09.240
We can't just wait.

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:12.200
What era is it? Still "Art above all else"?

00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:14.080
What matters now? Making money.

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:15.120
Then go make money.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:17.400
Don't hedge your bets and want it all.

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:19.160
You silly girl.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.040
What are you doing?

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.040
Playing hero to save the beauty?

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:25.160
- Showing off?
- Wang Qinsheng.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:26.040
I'm telling you,

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:27.560
I'll fight you on this.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.400
What are you doing?

00:04:28.640 --> 00:04:29.480
Are you still not...

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:35.240
Wang Qinsheng!

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:36.480
What are you doing?

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:38.440
Stop making a scene.

00:04:38.440 --> 00:04:39.360
If you keep this up,

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.600
the troupe has the right to...

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.440
Remove me!

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:43.040
Remove me!

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:46.280
You've pushed me this far.

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:47.880
Why should I fear?

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:50.480
What else is there to fear?

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:52.000
I have the right!

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.840
I'll show you what a scene is!

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:57.160
I quit!

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:58.920
- Troupe Leader.
- Look at you.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:04:59.760
I quit.

00:05:00.280 --> 00:05:01.480
He won't do anything rash, right?

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:02.440
Don't worry.

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:04.240
He's all talk.

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:15.260
(Ice pops and ice cream)

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:22.200
Sir.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:24.680
Open a Bingfeng.

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:27.280
Opener's here. Do it yourself.

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:51.400
(Qinqiang Opera Art)
The Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:53.680
is said to be a dummy.

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:56.480
Stop talking nonsense.

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:58.200
How could she be dumb?

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:01.400
She's charmingly naive and very cute.

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:04.320
Could a dummy sing that well?

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:05.760
I see.

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:07.160
What were you thinking?

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:08.480
I'll take it. Got any more?

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:10.840
Let me check.

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:16.800
No, this is the last one.

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.400
How much?

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:20.320
1.1 yuan in total.

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:22.640
Here.

00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:25.160
What are you doing?

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.480
Why are you yelling?

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:34.880
Move along. Keep it down.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.960
Sir, I left the magazines here.

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:52.800
Okay.

00:06:57.160 --> 00:06:58.200
This is juicy.

00:06:58.380 --> 00:06:59.780
(Yi Qin'e's Romantic Past)

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:01.640
She really isn't a dummy.

00:07:10.520 --> 00:07:11.960
My back's killing me today.

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:13.240
Work on it for me.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:15.280
Sure. Wait by the door.

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:17.000
Someone's inside. You're next.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.320
- Okay.
- Right.

00:07:21.300 --> 00:07:26.460
(Massage Room)

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:34.920
Yi Qin'e, the Little Queen
of Qinqiang Opera.

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:35.760
You know her?

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:37.240
What?

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:39.760
Listen to me.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:41.360
She's really something.

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:44.760
She rose from the mountains
to the provincial troupe

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:46.560
as deputy leader.

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:47.560
Do you know why?

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:48.800
Why?

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:51.600
I'm telling you.

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:55.400
They say she was barely a teen,

00:07:55.400 --> 00:07:58.360
mixed up with an old County Troupe cook.

00:07:58.400 --> 00:08:00.080
Later, to join the provincial troupe,

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:02.800
she dumped the guy she'd dated

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:04.080
for years.

00:08:05.760 --> 00:08:06.600
I'm telling you,

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:08.960
any man who gets near her

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:10.960
loses his head.

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:12.360
They all go crazy over her.

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:13.680
Know why?

00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:15.120
Why?

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:16.680
I'm telling you,

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:20.000
she's a nine-tailed fox from
the Zhongnan Mountain.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:22.080
Her tricks run deep,

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:24.760
especially with men.

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:28.880
What's wrong?

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.280
What?

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:36.800
Nonsense.

00:08:37.040 --> 00:08:38.160
Why are you tearing it up?

00:08:38.790 --> 00:08:39.760
That's nonsense.

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:42.600
What do you want? What?

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:43.440
What?

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.160
What do you want?

00:08:47.400 --> 00:08:48.240
Hit me?

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.360
What are you doing?

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:51.360
I'll beat you up.

00:08:51.970 --> 00:08:53.600
- I'll take you down.
- Hitting me?

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:54.440
I'll beat you up.

00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:56.720
Listen, just wait. This isn't over.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:58.240
You think you're tough?

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.040
Jerk.

00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:04.040
Sanyuan.

00:09:06.040 --> 00:09:06.880
Easy, easy, easy.

00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:08.440
Where are you hurt?

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:09.760
I twisted my leg.

00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:11.440
Hand me that book.

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:14.600
What even is this?

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:17.160
Those clowns.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:19.160
That's nonsense.

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:32.520
Dad, Mom.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:34.960
I'm here.

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:40.000
What happened?

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:41.160
What happened to him?

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:42.880
Why did you get into a fight?

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:44.400
At your age? You should know better.

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:45.720
Are you hurt?

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.080
What is this?

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:51.800
This...

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:54.000
Why is it so gross?

00:09:54.640 --> 00:09:55.800
Don't talk nonsense.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:57.160
Don't look.

00:10:00.280 --> 00:10:02.280
Good thing Qin'e is in Qianzhou.

00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:04.000
She won't see this for now.

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:05.960
But she'll come back.

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:08.520
Then don't let her see it.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:09.600
But how?

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:22.000
Hongbing, you're back.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:22.840
Auntie.

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:25.560
How's life in Chang'an?

00:10:25.560 --> 00:10:27.360
When do I get your wedding candy?

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:29.720
What candy? You never set me up.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.320
Like you need that?

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:34.720
Girls are lining up for you.

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:36.320
Enough for a whole company?

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:39.920
I'll find you Commander-in-Chief Mu Guiying.

00:10:41.560 --> 00:10:42.400
Commander-in-Chief?

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:43.440
Mom.

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:44.760
Mom.

00:10:44.910 --> 00:10:45.810
Ms. Liu.

00:10:46.770 --> 00:10:48.000
- Where's Mom?
- Hongbing's back.

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:49.000
Where's Mom?

00:10:49.780 --> 00:10:51.600
Here, take them.

00:10:51.760 --> 00:10:52.600
Upstairs.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:54.960
Mom, look, look.

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:55.960
I got you something.

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:57.320
Keep your voice down.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.560
Your dad's on a work call.

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:02.920
Fine. Look.

00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:06.720
A wool sweater from Chang'an.

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:08.360
Pretty stylish, huh?

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:13.480
What? Not happy to see me?

00:11:17.560 --> 00:11:18.400
What's up?

00:11:19.520 --> 00:11:20.520
I want to ask you.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:21.800
You and that...

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:24.120
Yi Qin'e...

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:25.080
Still keeping in touch?

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.120
Of course.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.320
Yeah.

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.480
I stayed in Chang'an for her.

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:31.560
What about now?

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:33.640
You two...

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:35.560
How far have you gotten?

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:39.880
You're not living together, right?

00:11:41.240 --> 00:11:42.600
I wish.

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:44.160
We're just dating.

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.360
I'm telling you, she's huge now.

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:48.720
Look.

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:51.240
(Qinqiang Opera Art)
She's in magazines.

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:53.240
If she weren't so busy performing,

00:11:53.240 --> 00:11:55.040
she would've come back with me.

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:57.440
Don't bring this stuff home again.

00:11:57.560 --> 00:12:00.240
You should cut ties with her.

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.280
What?

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.120
What did she even do?

00:12:08.280 --> 00:12:09.640
Why must I cut ties with her?

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:11.320
Why?

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:14.480
See for yourself.

00:12:15.460 --> 00:12:17.820
(Yi Qin'e's Romantic Past)

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:20.400
Where did you get it?

00:12:21.480 --> 00:12:24.080
Your dad brought it back after a meeting.

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:26.480
He blew up the second he got home.

00:12:26.520 --> 00:12:27.760
He forced me to call you.

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:29.480
He wanted you back right away.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:32.600
I kept saying you'd be back today.

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:34.640
That finally calmed him down.

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:36.480
Who's Pan Jinlian supposed to be?

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:38.640
This is all made up.

00:12:40.080 --> 00:12:41.280
There's no smoke without fire.

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.400
Where did it come from?

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:45.640
Who gave you this?

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:47.640
Look. This isn't her at all.

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.720
It's spreading rumors.

00:12:50.360 --> 00:12:52.080
Why didn't they spread
rumors about others?

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:54.600
What is that opera singer really up to?

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:57.040
How much do you know about Yi Qin'e?

00:12:57.760 --> 00:12:59.360
She's out in public all day long.

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:00.840
Who knows what she's scheming?

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:03.680
How did she get into
the provincial troupe?

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:05.000
What era are we living in?

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:07.600
How can you still think like that?

00:13:08.360 --> 00:13:09.920
Women hold up half the sky.

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:11.200
Chairman Mao said that.

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:12.080
Women these days

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:14.200
work and earn their own money.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:16.080
So everyone deserves rumors?

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:17.800
It's not your place to lecture me.

00:13:18.520 --> 00:13:20.280
Cut ties with that woman, now.

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:21.480
Come back to Beishan.

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:23.240
While I still have my position.

00:13:23.800 --> 00:13:25.320
I can still help you find a way.

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:30.080
Where did you get it?

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:31.880
Who wrote it?

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:36.600
I'll go find him myself.

00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:37.880
Liu Hongbing!

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:39.280
Ungrateful son!

00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:41.680
He was away for two years.

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:43.480
He came in and didn't call me Dad.

00:13:43.640 --> 00:13:44.480
All for that performer.

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:45.760
And he yelled at me.

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:47.600
Don't you call her that!

00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:48.680
Look at yourself.

00:13:48.920 --> 00:13:50.880
Is this how a son should act?

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:52.840
Dad only wants what's best for you.

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:54.680
I'll tell you the truth.

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:56.240
I love Yi Qin'e.

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:58.240
No matter what, I love her.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.240
None of you can change that.

00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:02.860
Hongbing, Hongbing!

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:03.720
Leave him be.

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:05.040
Let him leave.

00:14:05.320 --> 00:14:07.000
If you leave, don't come back!

00:14:07.840 --> 00:14:08.680
Ungrateful son.

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:19.800
Hongbing, what happened?

00:14:20.040 --> 00:14:21.400
Did you fight with your dad again?

00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:26.520
Stop sorting greens at my gate!

00:14:49.100 --> 00:14:53.180
(Yi Qin'e's Romantic Past)

00:14:56.740 --> 00:14:58.340
(The Secret Past of the Youth
Troupe Leader from Ningzhou)

00:14:58.340 --> 00:14:59.940
(The Youth Troupe Leader and Her Three Men)

00:15:23.380 --> 00:15:28.380
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang
Opera Youth Troupe)

00:15:30.160 --> 00:15:37.200
You trust the evil monk, not your wife.

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:47.080
Your wife worries through heat and cold.

00:15:47.080 --> 00:15:50.160
Your wife, for you...

00:15:52.120 --> 00:15:52.960
Every...

00:15:56.400 --> 00:15:57.920
Your wife, for you...

00:15:59.480 --> 00:16:00.360
- Sister!
- Qin'e!

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:01.210
- Qin'e, what's wrong?
- Sister!

00:16:01.210 --> 00:16:02.440
- What's wrong?
- Why did Qin'e fall?

00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:15.240
Fahai, Weituo.

00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:16.360
You two, go.

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:17.520
Quick, quick!

00:16:19.760 --> 00:16:20.640
Watch your step.

00:16:20.760 --> 00:16:21.960
Easy, Qin'e.

00:16:24.280 --> 00:16:25.680
Come on, sit.

00:16:26.160 --> 00:16:27.000
Hurry, hurry.

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:30.120
You get her some water. Now.

00:16:31.600 --> 00:16:32.480
You scared us...

00:16:32.960 --> 00:16:33.800
Troupe Leader.

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:37.000
Qin'e.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:38.920
Are you feeling okay?

00:16:43.320 --> 00:16:45.880
After these shows, I need a break.

00:16:46.640 --> 00:16:47.480
That won't work, Qin'e.

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:50.680
We've booked the later shows.

00:16:51.160 --> 00:16:53.040
They all came for Yi Qin'e.

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:55.440
What can the troupe do without you?

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:56.760
And also...

00:16:57.160 --> 00:16:58.520
The Youth Troupe...

00:16:59.040 --> 00:17:00.920
It depends on you now.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:03.520
Please hang in there, okay?

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:07.400
If you really can't, next month,

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:09.640
I'll let you skip two shows.

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:12.560
Forget it. You said that last month too.

00:17:15.280 --> 00:17:16.400
Let me.

00:17:18.180 --> 00:17:19.340
(Mianpi)

00:17:19.360 --> 00:17:21.560
Sir, liangpi to go, please.

00:17:21.560 --> 00:17:22.440
Sure.

00:17:39.400 --> 00:17:41.800
Fresh stock today. 8 mao each. Want one?

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:45.520
I'll take one.

00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:50.560
One second. Here's 2 mao back.

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:54.200
Take care.

00:17:56.480 --> 00:17:57.560
Sir, liangpi.

00:17:57.560 --> 00:17:58.920
- Coming up.
- Thanks.

00:18:13.880 --> 00:18:15.040
When did the magazine arrive?

00:18:15.040 --> 00:18:15.880
Just today.

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:17.040
8 mao each.

00:18:17.880 --> 00:18:18.880
How many do you have?

00:18:19.280 --> 00:18:20.120
They're all here.

00:18:24.120 --> 00:18:25.280
I'll take them all.

00:18:26.560 --> 00:18:27.840
Is this magazine that good?

00:18:29.080 --> 00:18:30.160
How many have you sold?

00:18:31.040 --> 00:18:31.960
Just sold one copy.

00:18:31.960 --> 00:18:33.120
A young girl bought it.

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.240
She was pretty.

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:36.000
She could rival Yi Qin'e.

00:18:42.260 --> 00:18:45.420
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:18:48.380 --> 00:18:53.180
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang
Opera Youth Troupe)

00:18:57.720 --> 00:18:58.820
- Make way.
- Have some water.

00:18:58.840 --> 00:19:00.040
Have some water. Take a break.

00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:02.400
She needs a break.

00:19:03.560 --> 00:19:05.160
Shrimp Soldiers and Crab Generals, come.

00:19:05.280 --> 00:19:06.760
Hurry, hurry. Keep up.

00:19:14.280 --> 00:19:15.200
We want Yi Qin'e!

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:22.470
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:22.470 --> 00:19:26.650
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:26.680 --> 00:19:32.640
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:37.370
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:37.370 --> 00:19:42.220
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:43.120
Make way.

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:47.370
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:47.370 --> 00:19:51.330
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:51.330 --> 00:19:54.930
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:54.930 --> 00:19:58.740
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:19:58.740 --> 00:20:02.310
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:20:02.310 --> 00:20:05.490
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:20:05.490 --> 00:20:09.300
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:20:09.300 --> 00:20:12.620
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:20:12.620 --> 00:20:17.840
Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e! Yi Qin'e!

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:19.800
Great!

00:20:20.600 --> 00:20:21.880
Great!

00:20:23.520 --> 00:20:24.800
Here, just these few.

00:20:26.760 --> 00:20:28.040
How much for all of these?

00:20:28.120 --> 00:20:28.960
Twenty in total.

00:20:34.640 --> 00:20:35.480
Here.

00:20:35.520 --> 00:20:36.400
That's all.

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:38.040
What do you mean?

00:20:38.280 --> 00:20:39.120
Hold on.

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:41.080
Sir, hold on. Wait.

00:20:42.440 --> 00:20:44.160
Five yuan isn't enough.

00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:45.440
Close enough. It's only a few books.

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:46.360
They come to 20 yuan.

00:20:46.360 --> 00:20:47.680
Five yuan? No way.

00:20:48.160 --> 00:20:49.880
- I owe you.
- I'm taking them back.

00:20:50.160 --> 00:20:51.000
You listen,

00:20:51.200 --> 00:20:52.200
you're not taking them back.

00:20:52.200 --> 00:20:53.040
What's going on?

00:20:53.120 --> 00:20:54.760
- What?
- Grabbing books in broad daylight?

00:20:54.800 --> 00:20:56.040
So what if I do?

00:20:56.040 --> 00:20:56.880
What are you doing?

00:20:58.000 --> 00:20:58.960
He's grabbing books.

00:20:59.120 --> 00:21:00.160
I paid!

00:21:00.440 --> 00:21:01.520
Look what he gave me.

00:21:01.520 --> 00:21:03.080
What's wrong with five yuan?

00:21:03.080 --> 00:21:04.560
I told you, put it on my tab.

00:21:04.560 --> 00:21:05.960
Come on, hand it over. Pay up.

00:21:05.960 --> 00:21:07.160
It's twenty. You gave me five.

00:21:07.160 --> 00:21:08.200
Hey, don't go. Don't go.

00:21:08.240 --> 00:21:09.080
Come on.

00:21:10.360 --> 00:21:11.760
- How much short?
- What's this about?

00:21:12.040 --> 00:21:12.880
Fifteen.

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:17.520
- Thirteen.
- Thirteen?

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:18.360
Two yuan short.

00:21:18.960 --> 00:21:21.760
But with that many books, it's wholesale.

00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:23.560
Fine, fine. All right.

00:21:25.600 --> 00:21:26.600
What kind of person?

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:29.320
- Look at you...
- What a weirdo.

00:21:34.980 --> 00:21:38.500
(Yi Qin'e's Romantic Past)

00:21:42.920 --> 00:21:44.280
Where did you go today?

00:21:45.200 --> 00:21:46.080
Chang'an County.

00:21:47.080 --> 00:21:49.200
All the newsstands along the south road.

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:51.040
And bookstores. I hit them all.

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:53.080
I'm totally broke now.

00:21:55.520 --> 00:21:56.760
How many did they print?

00:21:59.160 --> 00:22:00.880
Tomorrow, I'll go to the print shop

00:22:01.360 --> 00:22:03.600
and destroy the whole lot.

00:22:08.080 --> 00:22:09.840
You believe what that magazine says?

00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:13.840
Believe it? Not a chance.

00:22:14.680 --> 00:22:16.200
Qin'e is such a good girl.

00:22:16.350 --> 00:22:17.240
Look at that trashy rag.

00:22:17.240 --> 00:22:18.400
Look how they wrote about Qin'e.

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:22.080
If I find out who spread this rumor.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:24.880
I'll make him pay for every bit of it.

00:22:27.240 --> 00:22:28.080
Good.

00:22:29.000 --> 00:22:30.560
I knew I had the right person.

00:22:38.180 --> 00:22:45.020
(Diaojia Village)

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:51.720
So is this true or not?

00:22:52.240 --> 00:22:53.080
It didn't happen.

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:55.360
An attempt.

00:22:56.040 --> 00:22:57.520
Master Song stopped it.

00:22:58.240 --> 00:22:59.120
Where's that guy now?

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:00.800
He ran off.

00:23:01.960 --> 00:23:03.240
No one can find him.

00:23:03.960 --> 00:23:05.840
You wouldn't know where to start.

00:23:07.400 --> 00:23:08.320
All these years,

00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:10.120
how that child grew up...

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.400
Only she really knows.

00:23:25.560 --> 00:23:26.400
Master Chen.

00:23:31.480 --> 00:23:32.320
Kid.

00:23:33.640 --> 00:23:35.160
Did you offend someone?

00:23:36.080 --> 00:23:36.920
What?

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:40.240
Sorting files, making tea for the superior.

00:23:40.600 --> 00:23:43.400
With her gentle voice and sultry eyes.

00:23:43.680 --> 00:23:45.480
The superior began using his power

00:23:45.480 --> 00:23:47.800
to land Yi Qin'e some key roles.

00:23:48.480 --> 00:23:50.580
- The investor invited Yi Qin'e to his...
- Stop.

00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:51.800
- This is defamation.
- Exactly.

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:52.840
Qin'e, don't go over there.

00:23:52.840 --> 00:23:54.320
- It's a smear job.
- What happened?

00:23:54.320 --> 00:23:55.240
Just don't ask.

00:23:57.760 --> 00:23:58.600
Move.

00:24:05.100 --> 00:24:08.660
(Yi Qin'e's Romantic Past)

00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:10.080
You must've crossed someone.

00:24:10.280 --> 00:24:11.120
Exactly.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:12.480
This counts as defamation.

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:14.280
- Qin'e.
- We should call the police.

00:24:15.080 --> 00:24:16.520
This has to be fake, Qin'e.

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:18.280
We know you're not that kind of person.

00:24:18.280 --> 00:24:19.120
Qin'e.

00:24:30.680 --> 00:24:34.720
A good name is a bill no one can change.

00:24:35.680 --> 00:24:40.440
A bad name is a shackle you can't break.

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:41.320
(Jiuyangou Village Committee)

00:24:41.320 --> 00:24:44.040
If that's really how things are,

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:47.320
I'd be willing to drift forever

00:24:47.400 --> 00:24:50.400
on this monotonous ocean.

00:24:51.400 --> 00:24:53.600
Where can I find a sturdy...

00:24:56.440 --> 00:24:57.560
sampan...

00:25:00.320 --> 00:25:02.880
I can only wander the streets...

00:25:04.520 --> 00:25:05.440
That's enough.

00:25:05.760 --> 00:25:07.180
- Stop counting.
- Nine, ten.

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:08.720
It's only ten bills total.

00:25:08.800 --> 00:25:10.720
Count longer, still won't be more.

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:13.000
Meager charity.

00:25:13.120 --> 00:25:16.560
My life is a drifting withered leaf.

00:25:16.600 --> 00:25:18.520
- You had Cungen broadcast there?
- My future

00:25:18.520 --> 00:25:21.120
- is highland barley with no edge.
- His sister's famous now.

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:22.160
The kid loves attention.

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:23.960
Let him show off a bit.

00:25:24.230 --> 00:25:27.240
- If fate is truly like this...
- Xiuying, what are you doing?

00:25:27.240 --> 00:25:30.640
- I'd rather be wild thorns.
- A sheep costs dozens.

00:25:31.000 --> 00:25:32.840
When the in-law mentioned it before,

00:25:32.840 --> 00:25:33.760
I didn't believe it.

00:25:34.040 --> 00:25:35.760
If we'd raised sheep sooner,

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:39.730
- Even if it pierces my heart...
- I'd be rich.

00:25:40.230 --> 00:25:41.750
- Blood burning like fire...
- Who knew?

00:25:41.800 --> 00:25:44.560
- Burning like fire...
- Our sheep are like Laidi.

00:25:44.750 --> 00:25:47.680
- Crawling into the roaring river...
- Treasures.

00:25:47.800 --> 00:25:51.850
- The body dies, the spirit won't.
- How is she?

00:25:52.720 --> 00:25:53.560
You miss her?

00:25:54.430 --> 00:25:56.880
- As the poem says...
- I do, but can't see her.

00:25:57.920 --> 00:26:01.200
I'll feed our girl's sheep some grass.

00:26:03.320 --> 00:26:04.680
Keep working, everyone.

00:26:04.680 --> 00:26:05.640
I'll read another one.

00:26:07.360 --> 00:26:09.920
Dinner time! Dinner time!

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:14.320
I need to take good care of you.

00:26:14.920 --> 00:26:16.960
You're worth a lot now.

00:26:17.560 --> 00:26:19.320
Just like our Laidi.

00:26:19.560 --> 00:26:20.480
Precious as can be.

00:26:25.040 --> 00:26:25.880
Mom.

00:26:27.040 --> 00:26:27.880
Mom.

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:36.080
Laidi.

00:26:37.960 --> 00:26:40.480
The thing is, she never goes anywhere.

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:42.120
Don't panic just yet.

00:26:42.520 --> 00:26:43.360
Well...

00:26:43.840 --> 00:26:44.680
He's here.

00:26:44.880 --> 00:26:45.960
Where's Qin'e?

00:26:46.760 --> 00:26:47.760
If we knew where she went,

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:48.840
why would we call you over?

00:26:49.360 --> 00:26:51.760
Think. Where does she usually go?

00:26:52.040 --> 00:26:52.880
Where else?

00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:55.360
She performs every day.

00:26:55.600 --> 00:26:56.560
Or she's training.

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:58.000
Or rehearsing.

00:26:58.000 --> 00:26:59.520
It's always the same routine.

00:26:59.520 --> 00:27:00.800
Think harder. Come on.

00:27:00.800 --> 00:27:02.400
How would I know right now?

00:27:03.360 --> 00:27:04.440
How about this?

00:27:04.760 --> 00:27:06.360
If we have no choice, call the police.

00:27:06.480 --> 00:27:08.360
Let them help us find her.

00:27:08.920 --> 00:27:09.760
Will that work?

00:27:10.680 --> 00:27:11.520
I'll call now.

00:27:12.520 --> 00:27:13.360
What to say?

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:17.040
Report it as a missing person first.

00:27:17.160 --> 00:27:19.640
The police will take it more seriously.

00:27:22.700 --> 00:27:24.880
- What?
- Can this phone call long-distance?

00:27:25.520 --> 00:27:26.800
Cuffs? Shackles?

00:27:27.520 --> 00:27:28.360
Shackles?

00:27:28.560 --> 00:27:29.720
Gold-plated cuffs?

00:27:34.960 --> 00:27:36.480
Hold on, I need to take this call.

00:27:38.600 --> 00:27:39.440
Hello?

00:27:40.320 --> 00:27:41.840
Is this Jiuyangou Village?

00:27:41.920 --> 00:27:43.440
Yes. Who's this?

00:27:43.680 --> 00:27:45.240
Never mind who I am.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:48.080
Get Yi Maocai on the phone.

00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:49.960
Why are you looking for him?

00:27:51.200 --> 00:27:52.560
Why so many questions?

00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:53.680
Just stay out of it.

00:27:53.680 --> 00:27:55.360
Go get him to answer the phone.

00:27:55.520 --> 00:27:56.480
And you call me nosy?

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:57.560
Then I won't get him for you.

00:27:59.240 --> 00:28:01.640
Fine, fine. You're not nosy.

00:28:01.680 --> 00:28:02.680
Tell me who you are first.

00:28:04.520 --> 00:28:05.640
My name is Hu Sanyuan.

00:28:06.360 --> 00:28:07.440
You know Yi Qin'e, right?

00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:08.760
She was from your village.

00:28:08.760 --> 00:28:09.760
I'm her uncle.

00:28:09.960 --> 00:28:10.800
Uncle.

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:13.040
Yes, her drum-playing uncle.

00:28:13.200 --> 00:28:14.520
You're my uncle too, Uncle.

00:28:14.520 --> 00:28:15.440
I'm Cungen.

00:28:16.320 --> 00:28:17.680
That little fool.

00:28:18.080 --> 00:28:19.040
Go get him!

00:28:19.400 --> 00:28:20.240
Wait a second.

00:28:24.320 --> 00:28:25.240
Laidi.

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:29.280
Tell Mom what's going on.

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:31.920
Don't sit there silent.

00:28:33.280 --> 00:28:34.120
Laidi.

00:28:38.440 --> 00:28:39.480
What's going on?

00:28:43.240 --> 00:28:44.600
Stop pacing like a hen.

00:28:44.640 --> 00:28:45.760
You're just circling around.

00:28:45.960 --> 00:28:47.240
You're making me dizzy.

00:28:47.840 --> 00:28:48.760
Go make dinner.

00:28:48.760 --> 00:28:51.040
Something must've happened to her.

00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:52.120
What could've happened?

00:28:52.200 --> 00:28:53.200
She's just tired.

00:28:53.360 --> 00:28:54.200
Go make dinner.

00:28:54.360 --> 00:28:55.480
Keep an eye on her.

00:28:55.480 --> 00:28:56.320
Okay.

00:29:06.040 --> 00:29:06.880
Dad.

00:29:07.400 --> 00:29:08.240
Dad.

00:29:08.520 --> 00:29:10.440
My uncle called. He wants you.

00:29:11.160 --> 00:29:12.000
Who?

00:29:12.920 --> 00:29:13.760
My uncle.

00:29:15.360 --> 00:29:16.640
This sounds serious.

00:29:17.560 --> 00:29:19.240
(Youth Troupe Rehearsal Hall)
Seriously?

00:29:20.560 --> 00:29:22.120
People still do this stuff?

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:24.920
Isn't it outdated? Ridiculous?

00:29:25.800 --> 00:29:27.280
This kind of behavior now

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:32.720
is outright spreading
rumors and defamation.

00:29:32.720 --> 00:29:34.120
You can be held legally responsible.

00:29:35.200 --> 00:29:36.160
Who did it?

00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:40.600
Come to the troupe office later

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:41.880
and explain yourself.

00:29:42.240 --> 00:29:43.120
This matter

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:45.160
will be settled within the troupe.

00:29:46.560 --> 00:29:47.680
Whoever could've done this

00:29:48.080 --> 00:29:49.680
must want to be the lead.

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:51.920
And has the best shot at the lead.

00:29:51.920 --> 00:29:53.080
If, after today,

00:29:53.960 --> 00:29:55.200
no one comes forward,

00:29:55.760 --> 00:29:58.560
I'll take it to the police.

00:29:59.320 --> 00:30:00.400
Do I make myself clear?

00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:02.080
Yes. Crystal clear.

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:03.080
Dismissed.

00:30:15.960 --> 00:30:16.800
(Rehearsal Hall)
Chu Jiahe.

00:30:17.560 --> 00:30:18.560
Come here.

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:21.520
I need to talk to you.

00:30:22.600 --> 00:30:23.520
Let's talk over there.

00:30:30.600 --> 00:30:32.160
Troupe Leader, what is it?

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.000
That whole mess was exhausting.

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:36.240
I just want to ask

00:30:36.240 --> 00:30:37.800
if you know who did it.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:38.800
I don't know.

00:30:40.040 --> 00:30:41.760
But why ask me specifically?

00:30:42.640 --> 00:30:44.120
You've been her classmate for years.

00:30:44.120 --> 00:30:46.360
You must know her best.

00:30:46.760 --> 00:30:48.080
That's why I wanted to ask you.

00:30:48.720 --> 00:30:49.560
Just say it.

00:30:49.600 --> 00:30:50.600
You suspect me, don't you?

00:30:51.680 --> 00:30:52.920
I never said I suspected you.

00:30:53.560 --> 00:30:56.080
I just want to know what you know.

00:30:56.560 --> 00:30:58.160
This is a very serious matter.

00:30:59.480 --> 00:31:00.720
I know it's serious.

00:31:01.080 --> 00:31:03.240
But I really don't know what's going on.

00:31:03.800 --> 00:31:04.760
I also want to ask,

00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:06.400
if the troupe catches this person,

00:31:06.480 --> 00:31:07.680
how will they handle it?

00:31:08.200 --> 00:31:09.240
If it were up to me,

00:31:09.520 --> 00:31:12.400
at least public self-criticism.

00:31:12.560 --> 00:31:14.960
Maybe even a major demerit.

00:31:15.120 --> 00:31:16.240
What major demerit?

00:31:16.560 --> 00:31:17.880
Send them to the police.

00:31:18.120 --> 00:31:18.960
Police...

00:31:19.640 --> 00:31:20.720
We can do that.

00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:22.280
Then go ahead.

00:31:22.760 --> 00:31:24.480
But I really have no leads

00:31:24.480 --> 00:31:25.400
to offer.

00:31:27.360 --> 00:31:28.880
But, sir, if you find out,

00:31:28.880 --> 00:31:30.080
please let me know, okay?

00:31:30.360 --> 00:31:31.200
I'm off, sir.

00:32:12.000 --> 00:32:14.120
What car is this? What car?

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:17.520
Don't touch the car.

00:32:17.520 --> 00:32:18.360
Are we here?

00:32:18.760 --> 00:32:20.400
Not yet. The house is up the hill.

00:32:21.360 --> 00:32:22.360
It can't go there.

00:32:22.360 --> 00:32:23.200
We'll walk.

00:32:23.360 --> 00:32:24.200
Come on.

00:32:29.680 --> 00:32:30.520
Laidi.

00:32:31.280 --> 00:32:32.120
Laidi.

00:32:32.160 --> 00:32:33.040
Open the door.

00:32:34.320 --> 00:32:36.200
The kid won't eat or drink.

00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:37.760
She locked herself in the room.

00:32:37.760 --> 00:32:38.760
Who knows what she's doing?

00:32:41.480 --> 00:32:42.320
Laidi.

00:32:42.480 --> 00:32:43.760
It's really no big deal.

00:32:44.520 --> 00:32:45.880
Don't take it to heart.

00:32:46.080 --> 00:32:46.920
Okay?

00:32:47.400 --> 00:32:48.600
Look, Hongbing is here too.

00:32:49.120 --> 00:32:50.320
Back in Chang'an,

00:32:50.480 --> 00:32:51.600
he took such good care of you.

00:32:51.760 --> 00:32:52.840
Now he's at our home.

00:32:52.960 --> 00:32:54.920
At least come say hello.

00:32:56.160 --> 00:32:57.640
What's wrong with my sister?

00:32:58.080 --> 00:32:58.920
It's work stuff.

00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:00.120
Don't press her.

00:33:00.120 --> 00:33:00.960
We'll talk later.

00:33:04.240 --> 00:33:06.800
Qin'e, it's me, Hongbing.

00:33:08.640 --> 00:33:10.120
I know you don't want to come out.

00:33:10.360 --> 00:33:11.320
That's okay.

00:33:11.640 --> 00:33:13.640
I know you can process this yourself.

00:33:13.960 --> 00:33:15.360
It's actually totally normal.

00:33:16.120 --> 00:33:16.960
But if you

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:18.240
don't want to come out,

00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:19.400
just say something.

00:33:19.720 --> 00:33:21.560
Then we'll know you're okay.

00:33:25.760 --> 00:33:28.860
If not, make a sound, okay?

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:30.640
Let us know you're safe, okay?

00:33:33.000 --> 00:33:35.500
- Is he Laidi's boyfriend?
- Not really.

00:33:35.520 --> 00:33:36.560
Then what is he?

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:37.480
You wouldn't get it.

00:33:37.800 --> 00:33:39.560
At my age? What wouldn't I get?

00:33:39.560 --> 00:33:42.120
Well, they're not always a couple.

00:33:42.440 --> 00:33:43.960
They can take it slow and see.

00:33:44.400 --> 00:33:46.320
You city folks make things so tricky.

00:33:47.480 --> 00:33:49.040
Qin'e, are you okay?

00:33:50.320 --> 00:33:51.200
If you don't make a sound,

00:33:51.520 --> 00:33:53.240
I'll keep calling from out here.

00:33:54.080 --> 00:33:54.920
Qin'e.

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:57.960
Qin'e.

00:33:58.880 --> 00:34:00.320
Qin'e.

00:34:02.600 --> 00:34:03.520
Qin'e.

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:07.080
As long as you're okay.

00:34:10.840 --> 00:34:11.680
Brother.

00:34:11.800 --> 00:34:12.920
Someone's spreading rumors.

00:34:13.160 --> 00:34:14.600
Why won't the superior step in?

00:34:15.080 --> 00:34:17.080
People can say what they want.

00:34:17.240 --> 00:34:18.880
And we don't even know who said it.

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:22.800
That's what comes from being seen.

00:34:23.080 --> 00:34:25.600
Wasn't the kitchen just fine?

00:34:25.720 --> 00:34:26.560
What's with you?

00:34:27.160 --> 00:34:28.280
You'd have her cook forever?

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:30.640
People need something to aim for.

00:34:30.720 --> 00:34:31.680
Didn't you say

00:34:31.680 --> 00:34:33.320
a state grain ration was enough?

00:34:33.320 --> 00:34:35.120
Right. Stay out of it.

00:34:36.080 --> 00:34:37.680
Everyone hits a rough patch.

00:34:38.040 --> 00:34:38.920
She'll get through it.

00:34:40.640 --> 00:34:42.080
I know that makes sense.

00:34:42.440 --> 00:34:44.000
I'm just worried sick.

00:34:44.040 --> 00:34:45.320
I can't help at all.

00:34:51.440 --> 00:34:52.280
Hongbing.

00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:53.760
Your ride looks really nice.

00:34:53.880 --> 00:34:55.120
Our County Chief rides in this car.

00:34:55.640 --> 00:34:57.200
Was it imported from overseas?

00:34:58.040 --> 00:34:59.680
How fast can it go?

00:34:59.680 --> 00:35:00.720
What does it feel like?

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:02.600
Hongbing, Hongbing.

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:04.200
Take me for a drive.

00:35:05.200 --> 00:35:07.160
Hongbing, you can drive this car.

00:35:07.520 --> 00:35:08.880
You must be a big deal in Chang'an.

00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:16.960
A big deal?

00:35:17.880 --> 00:35:19.000
Or not a big deal?

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.840
Others don't decide that, right?

00:35:22.040 --> 00:35:23.880
As long as we know we matter.

00:35:24.280 --> 00:35:25.680
Who cares what others say?

00:35:25.880 --> 00:35:27.120
Don't listen at all.

00:35:27.280 --> 00:35:29.520
Don't let it get to you, got it?

00:35:30.760 --> 00:35:32.080
Impressive.

00:35:32.840 --> 00:35:33.680
Hongbing,

00:35:34.080 --> 00:35:35.680
take me with you to Chang'an.

00:35:36.360 --> 00:35:37.280
What for?

00:35:38.280 --> 00:35:39.360
The city's better.

00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:41.080
My sister went to the city at eleven.

00:35:41.120 --> 00:35:42.160
I want to go too.

00:35:42.640 --> 00:35:43.760
What's good about the city?

00:35:44.160 --> 00:35:45.640
All you see is your sister looking

00:35:45.640 --> 00:35:47.040
all polished out there, right?

00:35:48.480 --> 00:35:50.200
But all the hardships she's faced,

00:35:50.520 --> 00:35:51.760
I've seen them all.

00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:53.440
It's been really hard.

00:35:54.400 --> 00:35:55.320
You never know

00:35:55.320 --> 00:35:56.680
what pain she has to take.

00:35:57.240 --> 00:35:58.240
I wish I could do it for her.

00:36:04.160 --> 00:36:05.000
Qin'e.

00:36:05.560 --> 00:36:06.400
Come out.

00:36:06.840 --> 00:36:08.200
Come out. I'll take it for you.

00:36:08.320 --> 00:36:10.040
Pretend I'm the one spreading rumors

00:36:10.040 --> 00:36:11.520
and slap me hard, okay?

00:36:11.640 --> 00:36:12.480
Qin'e.

00:36:12.520 --> 00:36:13.560
Let it all out.

00:36:13.600 --> 00:36:14.680
You'll feel better once you do.

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:15.640
Qin'e.

00:36:25.360 --> 00:36:26.200
Good.

00:36:26.440 --> 00:36:27.920
Qin'e, good smash.

00:36:28.200 --> 00:36:30.000
Smash whatever's still in there.

00:36:30.160 --> 00:36:31.200
Let it all out.

00:36:31.200 --> 00:36:32.280
I'll buy you new ones.

00:36:32.840 --> 00:36:33.800
Smash anything you want.

00:36:34.440 --> 00:36:36.480
Alright, come eat already.

00:36:37.160 --> 00:36:38.760
I can't eat. Leave me be.

00:36:39.120 --> 00:36:40.080
If you won't eat,

00:36:40.080 --> 00:36:41.440
how can anyone else eat?

00:36:42.130 --> 00:36:43.080
Go eat.

00:36:43.080 --> 00:36:44.240
This is for Laidi.

00:36:46.000 --> 00:36:47.320
Auntie, I'll give it

00:36:47.320 --> 00:36:48.160
to her.

00:36:49.680 --> 00:36:50.720
Fine. Leave him be.

00:36:51.760 --> 00:36:52.800
Give it to her.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:56.720
Qin'e.

00:36:57.400 --> 00:36:59.120
At least eat a little, okay?

00:37:00.880 --> 00:37:01.960
If you don't eat a bite,

00:37:01.960 --> 00:37:02.920
it hurts me.

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:08.040
I haven't eaten in a day and a night.

00:37:08.120 --> 00:37:09.440
You've gone even longer.

00:37:09.680 --> 00:37:11.440
How about this? Crack the door open.

00:37:11.440 --> 00:37:13.040
I'll pass it in to you, okay?

00:37:30.240 --> 00:37:31.600
If you don't eat, I won't either.

00:37:32.560 --> 00:37:34.720
I'll sit here and keep you company.

00:38:04.640 --> 00:38:07.040
Brother, I brought the kid a blanket.

00:38:07.080 --> 00:38:08.680
It's cold. Let him wrap up.

00:38:08.840 --> 00:38:09.680
Leave him be.

00:38:10.200 --> 00:38:11.520
He won't sit out there all night, will he?

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:13.600
If it gets Qin'e to come out,

00:38:13.960 --> 00:38:15.400
he'd sit there for life.

00:38:17.200 --> 00:38:19.600
I think he's a good kid. Really good.

00:38:20.040 --> 00:38:21.000
Come on,

00:38:21.480 --> 00:38:23.360
you haven't seen how annoying he can get.

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:25.480
Lights out. Go to sleep.

00:38:35.960 --> 00:38:36.800
Qin'e.

00:38:39.280 --> 00:38:42.000
The moon here is so big and round.

00:38:43.680 --> 00:38:44.720
Feels like if I reach out,

00:38:44.720 --> 00:38:46.240
I could almost touch it.

00:38:51.080 --> 00:38:51.920
Qin'e.

00:38:54.600 --> 00:38:55.640
Are you asleep?

00:38:57.280 --> 00:38:58.120
It's okay.

00:38:59.000 --> 00:39:00.680
I'll stay right here with you.

00:39:01.240 --> 00:39:02.320
I'm going nowhere.

00:40:27.360 --> 00:40:28.200
Qin'e.

00:40:29.880 --> 00:40:30.840
What? Are you hungry?

00:40:36.040 --> 00:40:37.560
Qin'e, what do you want to eat?

00:40:37.560 --> 00:40:38.400
I'll make it.

00:41:05.920 --> 00:41:07.160
(Romantic...)
It's all behind us now.

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:10.600
You've got me.

00:41:14.520 --> 00:41:15.480
No matter how big it gets,

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:16.920
I'll carry it for you.

00:41:37.000 --> 00:41:37.840
Look.

00:41:38.960 --> 00:41:39.960
The sky tonight

00:41:40.720 --> 00:41:41.680
is full of stars.

00:41:43.360 --> 00:41:44.560
Tomorrow will be clear for sure.

00:41:49.560 --> 00:41:50.400
If you can't sleep,

00:41:50.800 --> 00:41:51.960
I'll sit here with you all night.

00:41:53.400 --> 00:41:54.960
We'll watch the sunrise right here.

00:41:56.000 --> 00:41:57.000
East is that way.

00:42:02.440 --> 00:42:03.280
Qin'e.

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:04.320
Where are you going?

00:42:04.800 --> 00:42:06.320
Don't you want to see the sunrise?

00:42:14.200 --> 00:42:15.040
Qin'e.

00:42:15.640 --> 00:42:16.480
Slow down.

00:42:17.200 --> 00:42:18.040
It's pitch dark.

00:42:18.040 --> 00:42:19.280
I can't see the path.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:11.040
We're not in Ningzhou anymore.

00:43:11.040 --> 00:43:12.840
You're no longer the top dog.

00:43:12.840 --> 00:43:14.520
You spread lies about Qin'e.

00:43:14.520 --> 00:43:16.080
You messed with the wrong person.

00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:18.280
Don't act up without proof.

00:43:18.280 --> 00:43:19.520
Sanyuan.

00:43:19.590 --> 00:43:21.360
I knew it was you.

00:43:21.440 --> 00:43:22.760
Who has the better life?

00:43:22.760 --> 00:43:24.120
The answer is obvious.

00:43:24.120 --> 00:43:26.040
What I've been through all these years,

00:43:26.320 --> 00:43:27.600
only I know.

00:43:27.870 --> 00:43:29.680
It's time to move things forward.

00:43:29.920 --> 00:43:30.960
I think you're beautiful.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪